snippet.title: On Currency Ban, PM Modi Says 'This Is Biggest Cleanliness Drive'

localized.description:
Prime Minister Narendra Modi, who is on a three-day visit to Japan, today addressed the Indian diaspora in Kobe and said that currency ban was the "biggest cleanliness drive" taken by his government.
